      "acceptanceCriteria": "RH < 1.0 at all validated operating points; CFD-predicted NIH within 15% of measured NIH across all nominal test conditions.",
      "rationale": "RH ranged 0.79–0.93 across five nominal operating points. Maximum NIH prediction error: 11.4% (at 6 L/min, 3500 RPM). All acceptance criteria satisfied within the nominal range. Gradation 2 achieved."
