      "rationale": "Validation performed on the identical FDA benchmark centrifugal pump geometry used in the COU. Fluid properties, rotational speeds, and flow rates represent the nominal CPB clinical envelope (2–6 L/min, 2000–3500 RPM). The COU additionally specifies relevance at extreme low-flow and high-speed boundary conditions; validation at those edge cases was conducted separately in companion work (TR-2023-04) and is not linked within this package. The assessed nominal range is considered representative for MRL 2 purposes by the credibility assessment team. Gradation 2 achieved."
