      "rationale": "SST k-omega selected per FDA hemolysis CFD guidance and published benchmark studies (Hariharan et al. 2011). Giersiepen power-law hemolysis model validated for shear exposures 1–400 Pa in the nominal operating range. Model form uncertainty acknowledged to increase at shear stresses associated with extreme low-flow recirculation zones (>600 Pa), which fall outside the nominal validation envelope. Gradation 2 achieved for nominal range."
